	-	Renamed C<expecting> to C<plan> for consistancy
	-	Rewrote POD

0.03
	-	Rewrote as a sane object to avoid evil tie/Hook::LexWrap code :-)

0.02
	-	Rewrote so that it would cope with nested blocks

0.01  Mon May  5 21:28:59 2003
